If the situation continues to deteriorate and the increased sanctions have no effect on Iranians, Americans will face the very difficult issue of a resolution of the problem by the use of military force.
For example, it will be necessary to respond to this at the time when, according to Obama, America will come to the victorious withdrawal of the troops from Afghanistan.
However, each solution of this type will lead to a dramatic reversal of the Afghan situation.
