They adopt, by intellectual comfort, the old life-threatening theory, recently reactivated by the "uniane-neurosciences" and widely disseminated, on their own, by the institutes of studies and the media.
Thus, by suggesting that it is possible to handle the "leviers" (sic) of the executives' engagement, a recent investigation of Ipsos published in Le Figaro.fr comforts leaders in a position of mechanical governance, inadequate to today's world.
Identify and measure mobilization factors
On the contrary, the managerial revolution necessary for the proper functioning of modern enterprises, involves adopting a finalist vision of human behaviour.
